{% include 'style.html.twig' %}

<div class="g5i">
    <h1>
        <span class="g5-title">{{ name }} Template Installed</span>
        <span class="g5-info">v{{ version }} / <span class="g5-info-date">{{ date }}</span></span>
    </h1>

    <p>By Installing Sample Data a new Home menu item will be created. The Home menu item and this template will be set as default. <br/>Other sample pages will be created as well. Click the button below to proceed.</p>

    <div class="g5-actions">
        <a href="{{ install_url }}" class="g5-button sample-data"><span class="g5-icon icon-cube"></span> Install Sample Data</a>
        <a href="{{ edit_url }}" class="g5-button config-layout"><span class="g5-icon icon-cogs"></span> Configure {{ name }}</a>
    </div>

    <div class="joomlead-info">
        Carefully crafted by <a href="https://joomlead.com" target="_blank">JoomLead</a>. Hi-quality Joomla Templates & Gantry 5 Particles
